description: This file defines the interface and a sample stub implementation for a Bluetooth Control module within the WPEFramework project. It includes class declarations, method signatures for Bluetooth operations, event registration, and notification mechanisms. The file serves as an interface for managing Bluetooth devices, adapters, and related events.
